{"tid":2357270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共外交部：美媒對香港及美國示威用詞截然不同令人深思","createTime":"2021-01-07T10:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T10:22:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a86c1776b9aac9aafac8eb030d1a7c0a15f3ed","tid":2357270,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:01:11.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中國外交部回應，美國總統特朗普支持者闖入國會大樓事件。<br />\n<br />\n發言人華春瑩表示，希望美國人民能盡快享有和平、穩定和安全，並質問為何美國一些人士和媒體對2019年香港修例風波中，激進示威者暴力衝擊立法會大樓、暴力破壞和襲擊警察，做出的反應是截然不同。<br />\n<br />\n她稱，現在美國主流媒體眾口一詞譴責，稱今次為暴力事件、暴徒、極端分子，當年卻以「美麗風景線」形容香港，把激進示威者美化成「民族英雄」；這種用詞的截然不同和背後的原因令人深思，值得進行嚴肅和深刻反思。"},{"pid":"6f489839f56a61c9981bb9f240bc598216cc4293","tid":2357270,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=419386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419386&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=3c4f68d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419386&h=321a49dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=419386</a>"},{"pid":"0ed4945e11fe7c1417236e01f05b613c1b9f4777","tid":2357270,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"香港人示威有冇喺現場殺過人？<br />\n香港有人用槍威脅其他人？<br />\n希望支國唔好將香港示威遊行集會嘅情況扭曲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李伯盧被拉咁大件事冇人講!?!?!?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2356503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2356503</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}